high_descs: Go forward to the counter one the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the gray knife near the left of the microwave.
Turn right and go to the front left side of the white table on the left.
Slice the potato near the back of the table.
Turn left and go back to the counter with the microwave
Place the knife behind the white cup inside the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the front left side of white table on the left.
Pick up one slice of the potato.
Turn left and go to the front of the  sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink under running water and take it out.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the right front corner inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a step left toward the sink and back to the microwave.
Pick up the knife next to the microwave on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the other side of the refrigerator.
Cut up the potato on the table.
Turn left and walk back toward the sink and turn right to the microwave.
Open the microwave door.  Put the knife in the back of the microwave, behind the eggs.
Close the microwave door.  Turn right and walk back to the other side of the refrigerator.  Turn left toward the table.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn left and walk toward the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink next to the apple.  Turn on the water and fill up the sink.  Turn off the water and drain the sink.  Pick up the slice of potato.
Turn to the right facing the microwave.
Open up the microwave door.  Put the slice of potato to the right of the eggs.  Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, clean it, and put in microwave to heat up.

high_descs: Go to the microwave
Grab the knife that is to the left of the microwave
Turn right and stop at the white table
Cut the potato on the table into slices
Turn left and go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn right and go to the white table
Grab a potato slice off of the table
Turn left and go to the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and then take it out
Turn right and go to the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean sliced potato in the microwave
